cst:
  root:
    kind: Root
    children:
      - kind: EndOfLineComment
        text: "' This is the Mk2 new format for database,"
      - kind: Newline
        text: "\r\n"
      - kind: EndOfLineComment
        text: "' to replace the access database for help file, as primary target"
      - kind: Newline
        text: "\r\n"
      - kind: OptionStatement
        children:
          - kind: OptionKeyword
            text: Option
          - kind: Whitespace
            text: " "
          - kind: ExplicitKeyword
            text: Explicit
          - kind: Newline
            text: "\r\n"
      - kind: EndOfLineComment
        text: "' this is the file id, where we place as first 16 bytes"
      - kind: Newline
        text: "\r\n"
      - kind: DimStatement
        children:
          - kind: ConstKeyword
            text: Const
          - kind: Whitespace
            text: " "
          - kind: Identifier
            text: b4
          - kind: Whitespace
            text: " "
          - kind: EqualityOperator
            text: "="
          - kind: Whitespace
            text: " "
          - kind: StringLiteralExpression
            children:
              - kind: StringLiteral
                text: "\"mk2-0001\""
          - kind: Whitespace
            text: " "
          - kind: EndOfLineComment
            text: "' these the first 16 bytes, as utf16le, type and version"
          - kind: Newline
            text: "\r\n"
      - kind: EndOfLineComment
        text: "' this is the verification code, so we have to check this, written as 16bytes"
      - kind: Newline
        text: "\r\n"
      - kind: DimStatement
        children:
          - kind: ConstKeyword
            text: Const
          - kind: Whitespace
            text: " "
          - kind: Identifier
            text: magic
          - kind: Whitespace
            text: " "
          - kind: EqualityOperator
            text: "="
          - kind: Whitespace
            text: " "
          - kind: StringLiteralExpression
            children:
              - kind: StringLiteral
                text: "\"{336C0F04-D0E4-7DF9-3F2B-E592A9936DE3}\""
          - kind: Newline
            text: "\r\n"
      - kind: EndOfLineComment
        text: "' then then GUID for the base written from 33 byte in file."
      - kind: Newline
        text: "\r\n"
      - kind: EndOfLineComment
        text: "' If this change, then we can't read or write to base, until we get the schema of the base."
      - kind: Newline
        text: "\r\n"
      - kind: EndOfLineComment
        text: "' This can be change if we open the base for exclusive work"
      - kind: Newline
        text: "\r\n"
      - kind: EndOfLineComment
        text: "' so every time we open the base for shared use,"
      - kind: Newline
        text: "\r\n"
      - kind: EndOfLineComment
        text: "' we look the GUID if it is the same as the one we have here"
      - kind: Newline
        text: "\r\n"
      - kind: EndOfLineComment
        text: "' if is the same, means that we have the proper schema"
      - kind: Newline
        text: "\r\n"
      - kind: EndOfLineComment
        text: "' When we use in memory base, we can do anything, but the GUID may change frequently"
      - kind: Newline
        text: "\r\n"
      - kind: EndOfLineComment
        text: "' So when we place the in memory base to a file, we set the last Guid."
      - kind: Newline
        text: "\r\n"
      - kind: EndOfLineComment
        text: "' this is the procedure when we define the base."
      - kind: Newline
        text: "\r\n"
      - kind: EndOfLineComment
        text: "' The actuall save of base happen when we close the base, with the option to save to file."
      - kind: Newline
        text: "\r\n"
      - kind: Newline
        text: "\r\n"
      - kind: EndOfLineComment
        text: "' Basic operations are: Open Base from file"
      - kind: Newline
        text: "\r\n"
      - kind: EndOfLineComment
        text: "' (this return to Open Base In Memory, and set the flag SaveAtClose)"
      - kind: Newline
        text: "\r\n"
      - kind: EndOfLineComment
        text: "' Open Base In Memory. This is for temporary use, as a record set"
      - kind: Newline
        text: "\r\n"
      - kind: EndOfLineComment
        text: "' We can populate records in a Base in memory, opening a Base from File (as source), and then"
      - kind: Newline
        text: "\r\n"
      - kind: EndOfLineComment
        text: "' we setup the query string from source, and we make a list of records as the output of query execution"
      - kind: Newline
        text: "\r\n"
      - kind: EndOfLineComment
        text: "' this list of records marshal the source to get a field row (the record), then using the"
      - kind: Newline
        text: "\r\n"
      - kind: Newline
        text: "\r\n"
